==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[sparrowfart]]; [[sparrow fart]]; [[sparrow's fart]]

===Etymology===
The time of day when the birds (including sparrows) first wake up, and presumably fart.

===Noun===
'''[[sparrow]]-[[fart]]'''

# Very early in the day; [[dawn]]; ''(Australian)''

